DADDY DID NOTHING:

Who&#039;s hiding what? Aaron came home from work one day to discover that his daughter had been molested. But this story would take a turn when police then turned their investigation toward Aaron himself! Someone&#039;s not telling the truth, but these lies wont fool Steve!
